data.description: Sellers are in the process of having property rezoned commercial to match the surrounding properties. This property has road frontage on the new Ranch Road Extension that connects to the Hwy 70 and Hwy 42 East intersection. View photos to see map of road extension. Sheetz gas station is right diagonal from this property. This property along with the property located at 1229 Tulip Street would provide .97 plus .52 acres and road frontage to the new road by Sheetz which is under construction now.
